{"word":"Tests, Spiritual","slug":"tests,-spiritual","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Tests, Spiritual</b> - <b>(A) DIVINE METHODS</b> used for testing believers<p/><b>By Demanding Great Sacrifices</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=22&verse=1'>Gen 22:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=20&verse=20'>Exo 20:20</a><p/><b>By Leading Men in a Difficult Way</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=8&verse=2'>Deu 8:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=13&verse=3'>Deu 13:3</a><p/><b>By Giving Opportunities for Choice</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=3&verse=5'>1Ki 3:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=32&verse=31'>2Ch 32:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=7&verse=9'>Psa 7:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=11&verse=5'>Psa 11:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=17&verse=3'>Psa 17:3</a><p/><b>By Proposing Hard Tasks</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=6&verse=5'>Joh 6:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=6&verse=6'>Joh 6:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=11&verse=6'>Joh 11:6</a><p/><b>By Permitting Men to Suffer</b> when in the Pathway of Duty<p/>(Paul and Silas)<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=16&verse=23'>Act 16:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=16&verse=24'>Act 16:24</a><p/><b>By Permitting Temptation</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=59&chapter=1&verse=2'>Jas 1:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=59&chapter=1&verse=3'>Jas 1:3</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Life Tested, LIFE<p/>Chastisement, AFFLICTIONS<p/><b>(B) DIVINE DELAYS,</b> try men's courage and patience<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=13&verse=1'>Psa 13:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=40&verse=17'>Psa 40:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=69&verse=3'>Psa 69:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=119&verse=82'>Psa 119:82</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=11&verse=6'>Joh 11:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=11&verse=21'>Joh 11:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=59&chapter=5&verse=7'>Jas 5:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=61&chapter=3&verse=9'>2Pe 3:9</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Trial Prolonged, AFFLICTIONS<p/>Waiting for God, PATIENCE<p/><b>(C) FAITH TESTED,</b> examples of<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=22&verse=2'>Ge 22:2</a><p/>By a strange plan of campaign<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=6&verse=3'>Jos 6:3</a><p/>By reducing a general's army<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=7&verse=7'>Jud 7:7</a><p/>By requiring dependence upon a poor widow<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=17&verse=9'>1Ki 17:9</a><p/>By demanding the last morsel of bread<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=17&verse=13'>1Ki 17:13</a><p/>By requiring, what appeared to be, useless work<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=3&verse=6'>2Ki 3:6</a><p/>By requiring extensive preparation with no blessing in sight<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=4&verse=3'>2Ki 4:3</a><p/>Other examples of<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=9&verse=28'>Mat 9:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=7&verse=27'>Mar 7:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=8'>Heb 11:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=17'>Heb 11:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=36'>Heb 11:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=59&chapter=1&verse=3'>Jas 1:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=60&chapter=1&verse=7'>1Pe 1:7</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Life Tested, LIFE<p/>Chastisement, AFFLICTIONS"}]}